### 1. 按题目查询测试用例列表（管理员）
# 测试场景：获取某题全部测例；需先「管理员登录」
GET http://localhost:8080/api/testcase/problem/{{problemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. 批量创建测试用例（管理员）
# 测试场景：为题目新增测例，返回新建 id 列表；problemId 改为实际题目 id
POST http://localhost:8080/api/testcase/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "testCaseList": [
    {
      "problemId": {{problemId}},
      "input": "1 2\n",
      "output": "3\n"
    },
    {
      "problemId": {{problemId}},
      "input": "100 200\n",
      "output": "300\n"
    }
  ]
}

> {%
  if (response.status === 200 && response.body.testCaseList && response.body.testCaseList.length > 0) {
    client.global.set("testCaseId", String(response.body.testCaseList[0]));
  }
%}

### 3. 更新测试用例（管理员）
# 测试场景：修改指定测例输入输出；testCaseId、problemId 需为库中真实值
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/testcase/{{testCaseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "problemId": {{problemId}},
  "input": "3 4\n",
  "output": "7\n"
}

### 4. 创建测例失败 - 普通用户无权限
POST http://localhost:8080/api/testcase/create
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "testCaseList": [
    {
      "problemId": 1,
      "input": "1\n",
      "output": "1\n"
    }
  ]
}

### 5. 删除测试用例（管理员）
# 测试场景：删除单个测例；请使用测试专用 testCaseId
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/testcase/{{testCaseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
